### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

@contentType = application/json

### The basic request
{{baseUrl}}

### Find All Tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks


### Find One Task
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/d5f6acd4-14ba-456f-9134-89186f8b5a78


### Create a Task
# @name createTask
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Learn NestJs",
  "description": "Complete the NestJs Course",
  "status": "OPEN"
}

### Set the task id
@taskId = {{ createTask.response.body.id }}

### Validation error - status is incorrect
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "",
  "description": "Complete the NestJs Course",
  "status": "XXX"
}

### Update a task
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Delete a Task
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
